<span id="freeTextContainer9267082492042589555">I really don&apos;t see the appeal. It was too strange and I could not begin to understand what the author wanted to tell me. Maybe I&apos;m missing the whole point of the book (actually, it feels like there wasn&apos;t one). Maybe it was spoiled for me by so many people telling me how great it is. I didn&apos;t think it was great at all and I had to force myself to finish it, which is why it took me 8 days. I don&apos;t think I&apos;ll be reading it again. Sorry, Boris.</span>
  <span id="freeText9267082492042589555" style="display:none">I really don't see the appeal. It was too strange and I could not begin to understand what the author wanted to tell me. Maybe I'm missing the whole point of the book (actually, it feels like there wasn't one). Maybe it was spoiled for me by so many people telling me how great it is. I didn't think it was great at all and I had to force myself to finish it, which is why it took me 8 days. I don't think I'll be reading it again. Sorry, Boris.</span>
